edu.cornell.gdiac.starstruck

Class Starstruck

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.badlogic.gdx.Game
      • edu.cornell.gdiac.starstruck.Starstruck
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.badlogic.gdx.ApplicationListener, ScreenListener

    public class Starstruck
extends com.badlogic.gdx.Game
implements ScreenListener
    Root class for a LibGDX. This class is technically not the ROOT CLASS. Each platform has another class above this (e.g. PC games use DesktopLauncher) which serves as the true root. However, those classes are unique to each platform, while this class is the same across all plaforms. In addition, this functions as the root class all intents and purposes, and you would draw it as a root class in an architecture specification.
